			title: "Together ✦"
			subtitle: "This is what the pack was for"
			description: [
				"§6This is the Bonus Chapter completion quest.§r"
				"§fNo crafting required. No boss to kill."
				""
				"§eInstructions:§r"
				"§7• §eFind a place§7 in the world that you all built or contributed to."
				"§7• §eSit down§7 (Supplementaries Seat, Decorative Blocks chair)."
				"§7• §eStay for 60 seconds§7 and actually look at what you made."
				""
				"§eSuggested locations:§r"
				"§7• §eThe Central Kitchen§7 — watch the Create line run."
				"§7• §eTrophy Room§7 — all six Twilight trophies glowing."
				"§7• §eColony Overview§7 — watch citizens walk to work."
				"§7• §eYour first base§7 — wherever it was, whatever it was."
				""
				"§eThis world took§r"
				"§7hours of exploration, hundreds of crafts, a few arguments about"
				"§7where to put the Warehouse, and one near-death experience"
				"§7that is still funny when you bring it up."
				""
				"§7It is yours. You made it together."
				""
				"§eReward: 64 Firework Rockets§r"
				"§7• Launch them. All of them. Right now."
				""
				"§a► Sit together somewhere you built. Mark done."
			]
